Extended Cohn-Kanade (CK+) Dataset

The Extended Cohn-Kanade (CK+) dataset is a benchmark dataset widely used for facial expression and emotion recognition research.

ðŸ”¹ Purpose

Designed to support studies in facial expression analysis, emotion detection, and computer vision applications.

